<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361602" n="1"/>
      <opener><lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr>
            <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus <abbr>Ant.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelotti</rs>
                           <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></opener>
      <p><lb/>Credo Te, Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, et <abbr>Claris.</abbr> 
            <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruel<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> eius Filium</rs> bene valere.
            <lb/>Accepi <abbr>humaniss.<hi rend="sup">as</hi></abbr> tuas <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517025905501">litteras</rs> mense
                              <lb/><date when="1719-12-27">Decembris</date> scriptas, ex quibus intellexi 
      <lb/><abbr>Celeber.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> brevi esse absoluturum
      <lb/>Lection<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationis</rs> me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Si ergo est
                              <lb/>absoluta <subst><del>,</del><add>et</add></subst> correcta cum additionibus, et
                              <lb/>admonitionibus necessariis ipsiusmet In<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>clyti <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs> Tui, rogo ut quamprim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> fieri
                              <lb/>poterit eam optime conclusam, et tela
            <lb/>ceracea involutam transmittas <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Medio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lanum</rs> quamcitisime ad aliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Mercato<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem</rs>, qui eam accipiat. Statim ac mittes
      <lb/>eandem <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationem</rs> scribe ad me
            <lb/>nomen, et cognomen <rs type="person">Mercatoris</rs> ad
            <lb/>quem illam mittes. Nam efficiam ut <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">is</hi></abbr>
      <lb/>Marchio <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1221327275">Butintrochi</rs> (statim ac certior fac<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tus ero de nomine et cognomine <rs type="person">Mercato<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris</rs>) scribat ad e<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Mediolan<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> imperando
                              <lb/>ut eid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Mercatori</rs> prompte solvantur
                              <pb facs="1361603" n="2"/>
            <lb/>omnes expens<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, et ut mittat huc <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Vene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tias</rs> ad semetips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> eandemmet <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>n<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></rs>, sive fascicul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> quem <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basil<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>a</rs> accipiet
                              <lb/>a Te. Novi tu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> optim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> voluntatem
                              <lb/>mihi favendi, scio te esse quam diligen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in omnibus rebus. Tibi ergo
      <lb/>commendo me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></rs> ne pereat.
                              <lb/>Non parcas expensis, etenim persolvam
                              <lb/><choice><orig>Omnia</orig><reg>omnia</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi indicabis. Si tu, et
            <lb/><abbr>Illus.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> voletis scribere ad me
      <lb/>epistolas me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationi</rs> inserendas
                              <lb/>maximum honorem mihi facietis. Adjiciam 
      <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationi</rs> <abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">as</hi></abbr> Disserta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiones <abbr>Illustriss.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs> de <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_JAFFCHKU">Motu Muscu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>, et de <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_W6BHQDM2"><abbr>Eff.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Ferment.<hi rend="sup">ne</hi></abbr></rs>, quare
                              <lb/>si ille vult facere aliquas annotatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes, vel correctiones, rogo ut mittat
                              <lb/>ad me omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> volet; nam ego
                              <lb/>proximo Vere prelo committ<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> suas
      <lb/>et meam <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationem</rs>. Locutus
                              <pb facs="1361605" n="3"/>
            <lb/>sum de <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruele</rs> Tuo <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr>; illi Nobili
            <lb/><rs type="person">Viro</rs>, de quo scripsit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1343364833">Fabris</rs>. Sed non 
                              <lb/>invenio dispositionem pro vocando
            <lb/><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruele</rs>; Nobilis hic <rs type="person">Vir</rs> rerum
                              <lb/>Mathematicar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, et litterar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> cupidus
            <lb/>vivit sub <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patris</rs> potestate, ac propterea
                              <lb/>non potest, opinor, efficere quicquid
                              <lb/>vellet. Si accidet occasio <choice><sic>opportuno</sic><corr>opportuna</corr></choice> pro
            <lb/><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruele</rs>, admonebo, eamque
                              <lb/>accipiam. Interim rogo ut quam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citissime ad me respondeas indican<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>do nomen, et cognomen <rs type="person">Mercatoris</rs>
                              <lb/>ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> per Vestros Mercatores poteris
                              <lb/>mittere fascicul<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> sed rogando ut <subst><del>cit</del><add>cele</add></subst><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>riter <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Mediolan<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> transmittatur eo modo
                              <lb/>qu<subst><del>o</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></add></subst> credes tutum, seu tutior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>.</p> <closer><salute>Vale 
                              <lb/>Vir Amicissime, impera mihi, et fave.</salute>
                                    <dateline>Dab<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> raptim <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> <date>2 Martii 1720</date><supplied>.</supplied></dateline></closer>
      <postscript><p><lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr>
            <lb/>Salut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> dico <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> et
            <lb/><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patrueli</rs><supplied>.</supplied></p></postscript>
</div>
